  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  patients with narrow angle that need laser iridectomy and take anti- aggregative
             treatment

          -  over 20 years old

          -  patients who can stop their anti-aggregative treatment for 10 days

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  under coumadin treatment

          -  post ocular surgeries
